379
00:31:20,350 --> 00:31:23,480
Co?
Já?

380
00:31:23,480 --> 00:31:25,250
Já snad dostanu zimnici.

381
00:31:25,250 --> 00:31:29,470
Proč bychom to pak dělali?

382
00:31:29,470 --> 00:31:33,510
Na to si vůbec nepamatuji.

383
00:31:38,470 --> 00:31:40,500
Hej!

384
00:31:40,850 --> 00:31:42,390
Hej!

385
00:31:42,390 --> 00:31:44,960
