386
00:31:44,960 --> 00:31:47,270
Nic...

387
00:31:48,330 --> 00:31:51,240
- Ty sis prdl?
- Ne, já to nebyl.

388
00:31:51,240 --> 00:31:53,180
Jsem vyčerpanej.

389
00:31:54,210 --> 00:31:57,530
